attribs.name: repeating_action_-KEZxrPq2NVXxlKmwyFP_content
attribs.current: Each creature of it's choice within 120 ft on a DC 18 Wisdom saving throw or become afflicted with short term madness (DMG pg. 259). If a creature afflicted with short-term madness falls its saving throw, it becomes afflicted with long-term madness. If a creature is afflicted with long-term madness fails its saving throw, it becomes afflicted with indefinite madness. If a creature afflicted with indefinite madness fails its saving throw is successful, the creature is immune to the presence for 24 hours.
